SELECT course.title, course.credits, course.dept_name
FROM course
WHERE course.course_id IN (
    SELECT course_id
    FROM prereq
    GROUP BY course_id
    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
);

SELECT s.name
FROM student s
WHERE s.ID IN (
    SELECT s_ID
    FROM advisor
    GROUP BY s_ID
    HAVING COUNT(i_ID) > 1
);

SELECT s.name
FROM student s
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM advisor a
    WHERE a.s_ID = s.ID
) > 1;

SELECT student.name
FROM student
JOIN advisor ON student.ID = advisor.s_ID
GROUP BY student.ID
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT advisor.i_ID) > 1;
SELECT student.name FROM student;

SELECT student.name
FROM student
JOIN advisor ON student.ID = advisor.s_ID
GROUP BY student.ID, student.name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT advisor.i_ID) > 1;

SELECT course.title
FROM course
LEFT JOIN prereq ON course.course_id = prereq.course_id
WHERE prereq.prereq_id IS NULL;
SELECT title, credits FROM course ORDER BY title, credits;
